des: Motorsports News Briefing is another sports minded flash briefing from Jody Burnett founder of ButtonPushApps. BPA used the Motorsports Headlines public RSS feed found at http://www.espn.com/ in the development of this Alexa app. You can find me on Twitter at @IGSoldiersCoach @ButtonPushApps @WeDoAlexa
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
